profile:
Whether it’s a small shed or a 1500+ bundle building complex, Roof Top Renovators can handle the job. Our Renovators have been put to the test every year and have managed to put some pretty noteworthy projects under their belt. Sometimes its a 3 layer steep resheet that is quite frankly just a mess, and somedays its a walkable raised ranch with an amazing view overlooking the water. Everyday a new challenge arises and everyday we have an opportunity to challenge ourselves.

“We Take Pride In Every Nail We Drive”

“That’s something that you are going to hear alot when you hear the name Roof Top Renovators, it is not only our logo but the very foundation on which our company stands, every shingle we place, every nail we drive, every hip we cap – all with Pride!

Roofing is an artform just like framing, asphalt, flooring ect. They all involve a certain eye to make things look uniform and here that attention to detail is one of the most important precedents we carry”
services:
- Residential Pitch Roofing
- Roof repairs, 
- Commercial shingle roofing
- Free estimates
- Roof inspections
- Insurance reports
- Residential Flat Roofing
- Fascia
- Eves-trough
